ling Your Characters Is Traumatic: And It Should Be</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">February 7, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/karenouten/">Karen Outen</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/literary-works-in-which-crimes-are-a-means-to-understanding-complexity/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/02/sad-family-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/literary-works-in-which-crimes-are-a-means-to-understanding-complexity/">Literary Works In Which Crimes are a Means to Understanding Complexity</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">February 7, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/megannolan/">Megan Nolan</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/the-1931-murder-that-foretold-a-new-era-of-crime-and-corruption-in-new-york-city/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/01/gordon1-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/the-1931-murder-that-foretold-a-new-era-of-crime-and-corruption-in-new-york-city/">The 1931 Murder That Foretold a New Era of Crime and Corruption in New York City</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">February 7, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/michaelwolraich/">Michael Wolraich</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
